snippet.textDisplay:
🌍 🇧🇷 dax monstro demais !!

tradução 👇

Não consigo dormir,
fico pensando sobre isso.
E se, com tudo o que está acontecendo, o mundo realmente estiver chegando ao fim?
Então o que?


E se não for mentira? (E se?)
E se chegarmos ao céu e não entrarmos? (E se?)
E se chegarmos aos portões e vermos Deus do outro lado, e ele nos olhar na cara e dizer que, durante toda a vida, perdemos tempo?
E se não pudermos voltar? (E se?)
E se não pudermos refazer esta vida e tiver uma segunda chance?
E se a nossa felicidade futura for lembranças do nosso passado (Deus)
Enquanto queimamos para sempre assombrados pelas risadas do diabo? (Hahahaha)
Por quê?
Por que os afastamos? (Por quê?)
E por que os que trabalhamos para manter nunca ficam realmente? (Por quê?)


Por que nos concentramos no amanhã e esquecemos o hoje (Por quê?)
E sorrimos na cara de todos e tentamos agir como se estivéssemos bem?
Por que vivemos assim?
Por que odiamos?
Por que lutamos?
Por que agir como se houvesse tempo e tivesse mais de uma vida?
Por quê? (Me responda)
Por quê? PORQUE!? Por quê? Por quê?

Eu sou mais velho e procuro a verdade
Estou segurando minha fé em minhas mãos, mas a dor neste mundo está se soltando
Eu costumava ter muito a ganhar
Agora eu tenho muito a perder
Eles dizem que sou louco por procurando respostas


Eu digo que eles louco para não dar provas
visão é borrada, estou mais preocupado
que eu estou olhando para Deus para ver se a vida com ele é algo que eu ganhei
O diabo está assistindo ele é tryna recrutar ele está esperando, a cada passo
que eu' estou dirigindo esta vida na estrada para o inferno, mas eu não vou queimar, porra!
Sabemos a diferença
Sabemos o que está errado e sabemos o que está certo
Mas Satanás é forte, Deus, e a maioria do seu povo está perdendo a luta (Tentamos)
Então, e se falharmos?
E se não pudermos escapar de suas mentiras? (E se?)
E se não podemos mudar, e se ele ainda controla nossas mentes?
Para onde corremos?
Onde vamos?


Com quem conversamos?
Nós olhamos em volta e todos que vemos também estão perdidos (Foda-se)
E se a vida fosse apenas um teste que todos nós fazemos? (E se?)
E se você estivesse ocupado quando ligamos para você?

E se o inferno estiver na terra?
E se nascer está morrendo e o nascimento de morrer?
Isso significaria que a vida não é um presente de Deus, mas a maldição do diabo?
E viver era ser mau, porque as palavras são invertidas?
E se o diabo entrasse em um pastor e ele liderasse uma igreja?
E se procurássemos a verdade, mas não soubéssemos onde procurar? (Onde?)
E se os livros que eles disseram ler nunca tivessem sido suas palavras? (E se?)


E se nós escolhermos segui-lo, mas ainda tivermos esse desejo?
Você vai nos perdoar por nossos pecados e nos deixar entrar no seu mundo?
Deus nós nos portões (E se?)
Nós não podíamos ver, ouvir ou tocar em você, mas tínhamos fé
Sabemos que erramos, somos humanos e cometemos erros
Então, apenas implorando para que entremos e que você tenha graça (por favor)
Deus!
E se nós não quisemos dizer isso?
E se o lugar em que crescemos esquecesse de ensiná-lo?
E se nunca tivéssemos a chance de ir buscá-lo?
Então o que, então o que? (Então o que?)


Querida Família
Estamos em tempos assustadores
Ninguém tem as respostas
Apenas certifique-se de espalhar amor
E acredite
Meu nome é Dax

snippet.textDisplay: There are a lot of Christians trying to defuse this song. Dax had a very valid point “what if the devil lead the church” after all who are you to say he didn’t? Look at all the misery, harm, death, hatred, negative, discrimination, lack of care and being humans all due to religion. This world is a test Dax and I know you know it. There’s ways to prove it too, but it’s too tedious to try and get in a religious persons head because at the end of the day they’re close minded and don’t care about the truth. They care about their bible as if that’s going to solve the problems this world is facing. Not to mention the advancement of technology. I’d like to see if by the year 3000 religion is even still a thing. These books were written by man just with a few different prophets. Islam is the most hated religion out of the three main religions when the jokes on them as Islam is Judaism and Christianity only modernized due to the religion being much newer and therefore more advanced. What I just said here religious Christians still can’t even face it, but other Christians and practically every Jewish individual can. This world was destroyed by Christians so we demonize the most peaceful religion and turn them against the world as we strip them from their sources and blow up their home towns expecting them to rebuild it. This world is lost that’s all I can say at this point... try psychedelics and you’ll learn incredibly quick that these “holy” books weren’t sent by God as God would never have brought these down to earth. You must learn about the history back then men would be married to little girls. Men could easily rape women and no one gave a fuck as a matter of fact if the women tried to retaliate she’d get tortured to death. There was no real sanitation besides the Arabs (don’t even bother arguing do your own research and prove me wrong this is common knowledge). There was no real “system” not government or overall power. Just a bunch of lost souls surviving and acting like animals. Then a holy book came out and you must understand. A book like that written thousands of years ago if you simply just walked into the village with the book and showed it to the people most of them wouldn’t even be able to read it. So to have so many pages and for a book to be so PERFECTLY relevant at a time period they were in if man said “god spoke this” who the fuck is going to argue? I can elaborate much further into this, but it’s a shame how badly this world is lost with sheep everywhere. Hell you have poor people praying for their life to improve just for it to not improve and every little coincidence they thank god rather than understanding it’s a coincidence. Only certain people understand truly why religion was made and it’s crystal clear especially in the 21rst century. Fantastic song Dax I’m glad people are finally acknowledging and speaking out their truthful opinions. People are still to stupid to realize if you could build a cellular tower and travel back in time with your phone and keep photos on your phone and told everyone in the village you’re God and can literally even answer all their basic questions and even predict their future who the hell is going to doubt you? Religious people choose not to think like this because they’re trying to defend their religion at all cost completely unaware their contributing to the overall problem. It might be too late because humans would prefer now to be isolated than be peaceful. Technology is only making that peace even more difficult to obtain.... my generation is the last chance (2000 babies+) if we get sucked into technology and isolation then it’s officially doomed as corporations will continue to thrive (nothing is wrong with being successful, but you need to see how technology has negatively impacted us specifically our smart phones and virtual reality). I’m hoping for the best, but being realistic were probably fucked :/ hell people don’t even care about talent like they used to you can LITERALLY see the world caring less and less every year and you can even listen to music to prove my point start from the 60’s then make your way to now... it’s pathetic. Thankfully we have people like Dax and Hopsin in our life, but unless more people alike rise up they won’t rap forever... once their time is up we’ll be right back to the lost world of technology and being a slave to society then believing in whatever religion you want thinking God is really taking you more seriously in a church where your praying for change and hoping for selfish things rather than you proving how genuine and good of a human you are and in the end being judged. We as humans have destroyed our own planet and caused animals to go extinct I’m sure God is so proud of us. Then you have Christians thanking Jesus for everything when he wasn’t even the most important prophet. They believe he’s really Gods son lol then who the fuck are we? Gods testing toys? People don’t even realize if anything were all God and we all have the capability to become the Devil and sheep are in some cases angels and in others demons. Heaven is what you make of this life. If you’re successful you can have anything and everything you’ve ever imagine forever... how is that different than a religious form of heaven? If you break the law and commit heinous crimes you’ll go to prison and live a life of repeated misery aka what religion would call living in hell as every day behind bars fits the symbolism of being burnt to death just to wake up again to be burnt again aka waking up behind bars in an isolated system with like minded individuals everyday and every night while being shamed and an embarrassment to society. People still don’t even realize these common sense things lmao

snippet.textDisplay:
"What if we can't change? What if he still controls our minds? Where do we run, where do we go, who do we talk to?"

All valid questions. The answer is found in JESUS CHRIST.
Did you know the god of this world...of this age...is satan? He IS the (little g) god of this world, and we are each born under his authority. Get out from under that little g god, a created being, and get under the wings of THE CREATOR. Stop worshipping creaTION and worship the CreaTOR.
You're right...WE can't change. He (the enemy) DOES have control of our minds...our thoughts. You think all those lies you hear of "you're not good enough...," depression, anxiety...you think those are YOUR THOUGHTS?!! NO. THEY ARE NOT YOURS! They come from the enemy that prowls around like a roaring lion seeking who he may devour! It isnt called "a spirit of depression," or "a SPIRIT of anxiety" for nothing. Remember the old school cheer? "Weve got spirit yes we do, weve got spirit how 'bout you?!"
You better BELIEVE we got spirit(S).
THIS is where the grace of the Living God comes in....where the HOLY SPIRIT comes in and drives out the enemy...He drives out those other LYING spirits.
Our HUMAN NATURE is fallen...sin is as much of a noun as it is a verb. It is IN US; our code...our human nature...our very CODE is corrupted.
This is our FLESH.
Submit to the God who LOVES YOU.
Admit you know you are a sinner, with sin IN you...not just "bad things you do." It is SO MUCH MORE DEEP THAN THAT.
It is IN our NATURE because of original sin/rebellion! We inherited it.
So you START A RELATIONSHIP WITH the Living God...the Father of ALL creation THROUGH Jesus Christ. His is the ONLY name under heaven given to men by which they must be saved. He is our direct line to the FATHER.
Talk to Him! Start a RELATIONSHIP with Him! Ask for forgiveness, admit you need a Savior, and ask for the Holy Spirit to be given to you.
Your whole life, and perception of this sick world will COMPLETELY change. People believe THE LIE that they must change FIRST before they can know God. Lies!!! If that were the case, nobody could be saved. Impossible.
We get saved, receive the Holy spirit...AND THEN..and only then...can we begin to change. Instead of living in/for the flesh, we walk being led by the Spirit!
Get you some of this grace and LOVE! Dont wait, people! Time is running out to choose which side you will be on for yourself!
Choose the RIGHT SIDE...with Jesus Christ. He is the ONLY way, the ONLY truth, the ONLY life.
Get alone and talk to God. He loves you and wants a RELATIONSHIP with you!!
God bless us all, in Jesus' name.

Ps....It is singular... the book of Revelation is singular. It is "THE Revelation of Jesus Christ." 😁👍😁
